com.qoppa.pdf

Interface IEmbeddedFile


  • public interface IEmbeddedFile
    Representation of an embedded file in a PDF document. This interface defines the methods that can be used on an embedded file.
    Author:
    Qoppa Software

        byte[] getCheckSum()
                   throws PDFException,
                          java.io.IOException
        Get the 16-byte string that is the checksum of the bytes of the uncompressed embedded file. The checksum is calculated by applying the standard MD5 message-digest algorithm.
